Package: r2resize
Type: Package
Title: In-Text Resizing for Containers, Images and Data Tables in 'Markdown' and 'Quarto' Documents
Version: 1.3
Author: Obinna Obianom
Maintainer: Obinna Obianom <idonshayo@gmail.com>
Description: Automatic resizing toolbar for split-screen containers, images and tables. Most suitable to include resize functionality in 'Markdown', 'Rmarkdown' and 'Quarto' documents.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://r2resize.obi.obianom.com/
BugReports: https://github.com/oobianom/r2resize/issues
